(71356, 129395, 0, 1, 'Escape', '', '2013-12-13 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 2, 9, 'Escape\n[Scene1:Escaping]\n\nExhausted and bleeding\nFinally escaped from the bullies\nLast strength used\nDon''t know how far i can run\n\nThey yelled at me\n"No matter how far you run"\n"We''ll always find you"\n"You should just give up"\n\n[Scene2:Giving up my life]\n\n"Hold on,don''t give up" (No…I can''t)\nI fell down and closed my eyes \nPrayed for never coming back\n"Stand up ,move on" (Why…I can''t)\nA memory flash it hit my mind\nWho''s whispering i''m all alone\n\nI''m falling apart\nAn aching void in my heart\nMy beloved left me drown in this hell\nI''m coming right now\nLord will you accept me\nA child lost her way\nReady for her last breath\n\n[Scene3:Beating]\nThey found me in a faint\nI hardly defensed\nThey beat me with no retain\nI felt the blood out of my vein\n\n"So you''ve learn"\n"Escape is not an option"\n"Do your job then we''re even"\n"Or death is your destination"\n\n[Giving up my life]\n\n"Hold on,don''t give up" (No…I can''t)\nI heard gunshots and they were dead\nThe blood of them spurted on my face\n"Stand up ,move on" (Why…I can''t)\nI took a glance of the one who shot\nA foreign face i''v never known\n\nI''m falling apart\nAn aching void in my heart\nMy beloved left me drown in this hell\nI''m coming right now\nLord will you accept me\nA child lost her way\nReady for her last breath\n\nI''m coming right now\nWill you embrace me\nWith your smile that I miss so much\nI''m coming to you\nMy dearest you\nHold me like you used to do\n\n"Don''t give up my precious"\n"You''ve got a long way to go on"\n"We''ll always be with you"\n(I''m coming\nEmbrace me\nI''m so tired living\nLet me end this\nLet me be in peace)\n', '', 319, '', '', '', '', '貪婪黑洞', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-01-28 15:55:10', '2015-03-12 14:04:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
